c: 45
v: 11
t: "hdha alquran aldhy 'anzalnah ealayk -ayha alrswl- hudana min aldlalt, wdlyl ealaa alhq, yahdi 'iilaa tariq mustaqim man 'atabieh waeamil bh, waladhin jahaduu bima fi alquran min alayat aldalt ealaa alhaqi walam yusaddiqu bha, lahum edhab min 'aswa 'anwae aleadhab yawm alqyamt, mulim mwje"